HEADWORD: Bouilli
<hw>Bou`illi"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>bouillir</ets> to boil.]</ety> <fld>(Cookery)</fld> <def>Boiled or
